  "title": "Sales Admin Assistant",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for Experienced Candidate to join us for the below position:</p><p><strong>Sales Admin Assistant</strong></p><p>· Provide customer service and attend to phone / email enquiry as and when required</p><p>. Processing of Delivery Order, Job Order, etc....</p><p>. Prepare Quotation & coordinate with customers</p><p>. Update CRM system</p><p>. Coordinate with store on inventory</p><p>. Provide general administrative support to the sales and customer service team</p><p>including filing, data entry and document management</p><p>. Perform other ad-hoc administrative tasks as assigned</p><p><strong>Requirements :</strong></p><p>· Min Nitec/Diploma in Communication/ administration</p><p>· At least 1-2 years relevant working experience</p><p>· Must be a multi-tasker with good time management</p><p>· <strong>Full of initiative, committed, meticulous and able to work independently</strong></p><p><strong>without much Guidance, Good negotiation skills</strong></p><p>· Computer literate in MS office, outlook</p><p>· Those who can start immediately will be preferred</p><p><br /></p><p>Interested candidates may send in their resume via whatsApp at HP no:96518935 or email to: hr@puricare.com.sg</p>",
